[B]Directory Channel Building[/B]

[COLOR=blue][B]Directory:[/B][/COLOR] - Select local folder containing supported formats.

[COLOR=blue][B]Media Limit:[/B][/COLOR] - Set Channel Media Limit

[COLOR=blue][B]Sort Order:[/B][/COLOR] - Set Preferred Channel Sort Order

This channel type is recommended for media not found in Kodi's library only! ie. Custom Videos.
Directory search is recursion, all valid video extensions found in the root and subfolders are added.
http://kodi.wiki/view/Features_and_supported_formats#Format_support